283
00:21:28,785 --> 00:21:30,741
KANG JAE-HO

284
00:21:35,883 --> 00:21:38,531
Hello, I'm reporter Han Ji-won
from Korea Daily.

285
00:21:41,958 --> 00:21:45,359
