286
00:21:45,442 --> 00:21:47,348
It's me, Ji-won. Han Ji-won.

287
00:21:48,848 --> 00:21:49,899
Oh, right.

288
00:21:51,715 --> 00:21:53,916
- The editor of Ehyeon's magazine?
- Yes.

289
00:21:54,722 --> 00:21:55,633
It's nice to see you. Sit down.

290
00:21:55,716 --> 00:21:57,047
- Are you well?
- Yes.

291
00:21:57,130 --> 00:21:58,983
I'm filling in for someone last minute,

292
00:21:59,066 --> 00:22:00,958
so I didn't know I was meeting you.

293
00:22:01,041 --> 00:22:02,845
- Really?
- I better give you my name card.

294
00:22:07,362 --> 00:22:10,083
So you ended up
becoming a reporter after all.

295
00:22:12,049 --> 00:22:14,478
You really made it.

296
00:22:14,561 --> 00:22:17,102
I still have a long way to go.

297
00:22:17,185 --> 00:22:20,375
