Managing a business is hard.

298
00:22:20,458 --> 00:22:23,512
Being modest doesn't suit you.

299
00:22:23,595 --> 00:22:25,788
You need to be honest in an interview.

300
00:22:27,185 --> 00:22:29,579
You're exactly the same.

301
00:22:30,733 --> 00:22:34,051
You had such a strong will,
so I knew you'd become a reporter.

302
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,399
Did you stay in the States all this time?

303
00:22:36,482 --> 00:22:39,878
Yes.
Well, I had to since my business is there.

304
00:22:39,961 --> 00:22:43,388
I only make a short visit to Korea
when I'm traveling to Japan.

305
00:22:45,081 --> 00:22:47,780
What a small world we live in.
We ended up meeting again.

306
00:22:47,863 --> 00:22:49,238
You're right.

307
00:22:49,321 --> 00:22:51,947
Do you still talk to everyone?

308
00:22:52,849 --> 00:22:54,434
Yes, a few.

309
00:22:55,885 --> 00:23:00,705
While bringing up my company,
I had to think a lot and make decisions.

310
00:23:02,708 --> 00:23:06,011
Seoul is the world's
seventh largest megalopolis.

311
00:23:06,094 --> 00:23:07,708
Dear people of Seoul

312
00:23:07,791 --> 00:23:10,360
and party members.

313
00:23:10,821 --> 00:23:13,531
What we need is someone

314
00:23:13,614 --> 00:23:16,639
