and what drives us to grow.

315
00:23:17,453 --> 00:23:21,363
I'm young,
and my leadership is innovative.

316
00:23:21,446 --> 00:23:24,639
Please support Choi Ji-hoon.

317
00:23:24,722 --> 00:23:25,726
Thank you!

