DEMOCRATIC REPUBLICAN PARTY'S
FIFTH PARTY CONVENTION

319
00:23:28,009 --> 00:23:30,014
THE BIRTH OF A NEW KIND OF RULING

320
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:38,526
Choi Ji-hoon! Choi Ji-hoon!

321
00:23:42,094 --> 00:23:44,739
By the way,
when did you learn sign language?

322
00:23:44,822 --> 00:23:46,996
I was so impressed
while watching the video online.

323
00:23:47,079 --> 00:23:50,953
Countless people pressed like
on that video.

324
00:23:51,511 --> 00:23:56,548
You two are like Jacqueline
and President Kennedy.

325
00:23:56,631 --> 00:23:58,416
You're just like them.

326
00:23:59,165 --> 00:24:01,667
Please don't say something like that.

327
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:04,041
It might start weird news reports.

328
00:24:04,124 --> 00:24:06,601
Many things come into play,

329
00:24:06,684 --> 00:24:09,129
but the candidate himself
is what determines the election result.

330
00:24:09,212 --> 00:24:12,945
Yes. I'm trying not to think about it
in a complicated way.

331
00:24:13,028 --> 00:24:15,541
I have a concrete and clear goal,

332
00:24:15,624 --> 00:24:16,654
and that's what I'm enjoying.

333
00:24:16,737 --> 00:24:18,934
Yes, that's true. But I think

334
00:24:19,017 --> 00:24:23,679
your wife's support
really gave you a boost.

335
00:24:23,762 --> 00:24:25,507
If you have a beautiful flower,

336
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:28,381
you should take it around
and show everyone.

337
